  Locus:
    Page: 69
Title: Behind You
---
There is a wanting of God
so much
that you are willing
to forsake everything
godly to find him.
Ponder this,
the God who is beyond
what is godly.
Know this,
that you may have to leave
more than you ever imagined
behind.
